---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '@/components/sections/HeroSection.astro';
import FeatureGrid from '@/components/sections/FeatureGrid.astro';
import TwoBlockSection from '@/components/sections/TwoBlockSection.astro';
import CTACard from '@/components/sections/CTACard.astro';
import FAQSection from '@/components/sections/FAQSection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="What is Invoice OCR API? | FormX.ai"
  description=""
  canonicalUrl="https://www.formx.ai/solutions/invoice-ocr-api"
  showFooterForm={true}
>
  <div class="section product-hero bg-f0f4f9">
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-hero-wrapper">
        <div class="hero-content-block">
          <div class="product-hero-title paragraph-small">Invoice</div>
          <div class="product-hero-content-wrapper">
            <h1 class="product-hero-content-heading">Invoice OCR API</h1>
            <div class="product-hero-content-subheading">Easily extract data from invoices and integrate with ERP or AP Software to automate invoice processing.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-layout-vflex flex-block-86">
            <div class="w-layout-hflex action-buttons">
              <a href="/tools/invoice-ocr-api" class="button-primary button-left gray w-button">Try it Free!</a>
              <a href="/schedule-demo" class="button-primary button-left button-primary-shadow button-gradient w-button">Schedule a Demo -&gt;</a>
            </div>
            <p class="formx-portal-textlink">Need full workflow setup? Sign in <a href="https://formextractorai.com/signup" target="_blank">FormX.ai</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-layout-hflex icons">
            <div class="w-layout-hflex flex-block-27">
              <img src="/images/pages/solutions-hero-bannericon-free.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" />
              <div>100 free pages</div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-layout-hflex flex-block-27">
              <img src="/images/pages/solutions-hero-bannericon-creditcard.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" />
              <div>No credit card</div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-layout-hflex flex-block-27">
              <img src="/images/pages/solutions-hero-bannericon-lock.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" />
              <div>100% secured</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image-block">
          <img src="/images/pages/documenttype_kv_invoice@2x.webp" loading="lazy" width="2400" height="2000" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 969px" alt="" srcset="/images/pages/documenttype_kv_invoice@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/documenttype_kv_invoice@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/documenttype_kv_invoice@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/documenttype_kv_invoice@2x-p-1600.webp 1600w, /images/pages/documenttype_kv_invoice@2x-p-2000.webp 2000w, /images/pages/documenttype_kv_invoice@2x.webp 2400w" class="image-7" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper t-column t-gap-40">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper">
          <h2 class="product-2-block-heading">What is Invoice OCR API?</h2>
          <div class="product-2-block-paragraph">The Invoice OCR API from FormX.ai is a sophisticated tool that employs OCR, machine learning, and natural language processing to accurately extract crucial information from invoice images or files. This technology goes beyond simple digitization by transforming unstructured invoice data into structured data pairs, ready for analysis or integration into other applications.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper t-full">
          <img src="/images/pages/solutions_what-is-ocr@2x.webp" loading="lazy" width="705" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 705px" alt="" srcset="/images/pages/solutions_what-is-ocr@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/solutions_what-is-ocr@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/solutions_what-is-ocr@2x.webp 1410w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section product-section">
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-heading-content-wrapper">
        <div class="product-heading-wrapper">
          <h2 class="product-heading">How Does <span class="heading-gradient">Invoice OCR API Work?</span></h2>
          <div class="product-subheading">Utilizing the FormX.ai Invoice OCR API is straightforward thanks to our pre-built invoice extractor. Follow these steps:</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-content-wrapper">
          <div class="_3-block-grid">
            <div class="plain-svg-card card-bg-f7f8fc p-48">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-left">
                <img src="/images/pages/invoice.svg" loading="lazy" width="80" alt="" class="card-svg xs" />
              </div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text plain-svg-card-align-left">Create from the Pre-built Extractor</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description plain-svg-card-align-left">Leverage our existing invoice extractor to accelerate the process.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plain-svg-card card-bg-f7f8fc p-48">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-left">
                <img src="/images/pages/invoice-2.svg" loading="lazy" width="80" alt="" class="card-svg xs" />
              </div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text plain-svg-card-align-left">Upload Your Documents</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description plain-svg-card-align-left">Easily upload your invoice images or files.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plain-svg-card card-bg-f7f8fc p-48">
              <div class="card-svg-block svg-left">
                <img src="/images/pages/invoice-3.svg" loading="lazy" width="80" alt="" class="card-svg xs" />
              </div>
              <div class="svg-card-content-wrapper">
                <div class="svg-card-title bold-text plain-svg-card-align-left">Test and Integrate</div>
                <div class="svg-card-description plain-svg-card-align-left">Verify the extractor's accuracy through testing, then seamlessly integrate the API into your system for automated data extraction.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <FeatureGrid
    heading="Turn Invoice Into Structured Data With Our Invoice OCR"
    bgClass="bg-f7f8fc"
    columns={3}
    cards={[
      {
        icon: "/images/pages/Group-239.webp",
        iconWidth: 128,
        title: "Improve Efficiency & Onboarding Experience",
        description: "Eliminate manual data entry with Identity Document OCR to provide better onboarding experience and improve operational efficiency."
      },
      {
        icon: "/images/pages/Group-240.webp",
        iconWidth: 80,
        title: "Improve Efficiency & Onboarding Experience",
        description: "Automate ID data extraction with our proprietary technologies to eliminate human errors and increase data accuracy."
      },
      {
        icon: "/images/pages/Group-241.webp",
        iconWidth: 80,
        title: "Decrease Costs of Manual Data Entry",
        description: "Replace manual data entry with Identity Document OCR to reduce unnecessary costs."
      }
    ]}
  />

  <div class="section product-section bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="container-default heading-content w-container">
      <div class="home-heading">
        <h2 class="text-center">Speed Up Application &amp; Verification Process Across Industries</h2>
      </div>
      <div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="_2-block-flex tabs-with-image w-tabs">
        <div class="hover-change tabs w-tab-menu">
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Public Sector</div>
            <div style="height:0px" class="hover-change-description">Streamline document handling and data extraction for insurance companies with FormX.ai. Protect sensitive information, automate outpatient claims, and analyze asset portfolios.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Finance</div>
            <div style="height:0px" class="hover-change-description">Automate data extraction from financial documents, enhance security with PII protection, and gain valuable insights for asset portfolio analysis.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Telecommunication &amp; More</div>
            <div style="height:0px" class="hover-change-description">Improve accuracy and efficiency in your retail business with FormX.ai. Automate receipt data extraction, centralize customer information, and make accurate product recommendations.</div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="_2-block-flex-image tabs w-tab-content">
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="w-tab-pane w--tab-active">
            <img width="600" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 600px" alt="" src="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp 1230w" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img width="600" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 600px" alt="" src="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp 1230w" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp 1230w" alt="" src="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp" loading="eager" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <FeatureGrid
    heading="Incorporate Invoice OCR API Into Existing Workflows"
    subheading="Any businesses that need to extract data from invoices can benefit from incorporating Invoice OCR API into their workflow."
    bgClass="bg-f7f8fc"
    columns={3}
    cards={[
      {
        title: "Accounts Payable Automation",
        description: "Automatically extract data from your invoices to automate your AP process."
      },
      {
        title: "ERP Software",
        description: "Integrate FormX's Invoice OCR with any ERP software to expedite your financial and administrative processes."
      },
      {
        title: "RPA Software",
        description: "Combine the power of Invoice OCR and RPA to automate invoice processing."
      }
    ]}
  />

  <FeatureGrid
    heading="Automatically Capture Invoice Data for You To:"
    bgClass="bg-f7f8fc"
    columns={3}
    cards={[
      {
        icon: "/images/pages/solutions_businesscert-icon-01.svg",
        iconWidth: 128,
        title: "Increase Productivity By 10x",
        description: "Invoice OCR can process invoices much faster and your staff is free from tedious data entry, empowering them to focus on other critical tasks."
      },
      {
        icon: "/images/pages/solutions_businesscert-icon-02.svg",
        iconWidth: 80,
        title: "Decrease Processing Costs",
        description: "The real cost of manual data entry can be staggering. Automating data entry with Invoice OCR to significantly reduce your operational costs."
      },
      {
        icon: "/images/pages/solutions_businesscert-icon-03.svg",
        iconWidth: 80,
        title: "Reduce Errors",
        description: "No more human errors caused by stress and fatigue as the entire process can be done without any human in the loop. Achieve high accuracy powered by AI & ML."
      }
    ]}
  />

  <CTACard
    heading="Automate Invoice Data Extraction with OCR &amp; ML"
    ctaSecondary={{ text: "Schedule Demo ->", href: "/schedule-demo" }}
  />

  <div class="section product-section bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="container-default heading-content w-container">
      <div class="home-heading">
        <h2 class="text-center no-wrap">Extract Important Fields from Invoices with OCR and AI</h2>
      </div>
      <div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="_2-block-flex tabs-with-image w-tabs">
        <div class="hover-change tabs w-tab-menu">
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Step 1: Set Up Your Invoice Extractor</div>
            <div style="height:0px" class="hover-change-description">On the web portal, you can create your own Invoice Extractor and select what data items, such as invoice number, PO number, vendor's address, total amount, and more, that you wish to extract.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Step 2: Test The Result</div>
            <div style="height:0px" class="hover-change-description">After creating your Invoice Extractor, you can upload a sample invoice image and check the JSON output to verify the results.</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Step 3: Integrate FormX with your AP Software or use the Desktop APP for Batch Extraction</div>
            <div style="height:0px" class="hover-change-description">Once you're done, you can integrate the Invoice Extractor with your ERP or AP software to automate AP processing. If you want to get a CSV file instead, you can use our Desktop App for batch extraction. Instructions can be found in our documentation page.</div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="_2-block-flex-image tabs w-tab-content">
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="w-tab-pane w--tab-active">
            <img width="600" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 600px" alt="" src="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp 1230w" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img width="600" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 600px" alt="" src="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp 1230w" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img sizes="100vw" srcset="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp 1230w" alt="" src="/images/pages/solutions_idcard-01@2x.webp" loading="eager" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <TwoBlockSection
    heading="Extract All Fields You Need to Process Invoices"
    body="Invoice fields that can be automatically extracted with our pre-built invoice model are listed below. Additional fields can be added upon request."
    imagePosition="left"
    bgClass="bg-f7f8fc"
    image={{
      src: "/images/pages/solutions_invoice-02@2x-6639c880.webp",
      alt: "",
      width: 685,
      srcset: "/images/pages/solutions_invoice-02@2x-p-500-6639c880.webp 500w, /images/pages/solutions_invoice-02@2x-p-800-6639c880.webp 800w, /images/pages/solutions_invoice-02@2x-p-1080-6639c880.webp 1080w, /images/pages/solutions_invoice-02@2x-6639c880.webp 1370w",
      sizes: "(max-width: 479px) 100vw, 685px"
    }}
  />

  <FAQSection
    heading="Frequently Asked Questions"
    items={[
      {
        question: "What is Invoice OCR API and how does it work?",
        answer: "Invoice OCR does more than simply converting images of invoices to editable and searchable texts. Invoice OCR is powered by machine learning and is capable of extracting data from invoices as key-value pairs and output structured data that can be directly imported into other software to automate invoice processing.<br/>"
      },
      {
        question: "Can FormX scan and extract line items on invoices?",
        answer: "Yes, our invoice OCR API is capable of extracting line items to show the name, amount, quantity, and unit price of each line item or product.<br/>"
      },
      {
        question: "Can FormX be integrated with other systems for accounting or robotic process automation (RPA)?",
        answer: `Definitely. FormX can be easily integrated with different systems or software, including accounting or ERP software, to automate data entry. Furthermore, FormX can also be <a href="/blog">integrated with the UiPath workflow</a> to bring our advanced extraction models into your robot process.<br/>`
      },
      {
        question: "What are the pricing plans of FormX?",
        answer: `FormX provides free trial for users to test out our features and process the first 100 pages for free. For monthly subscription, our Starter plan costs USD $299 / month, allowing you to process up to 3,000 pages. For enterprises with more documents to process, you may <a href="/schedule-demo">contact our team</a> for more detailed discussion.<br/>`
      },
      {
        question: "Is it possible to modify the results returned by the Invoice OCR API?",
        answer: "Yes, we've developed a tool called \"Formatter\" that allows you to add several steps to automatically modify the extracted data according to your needs. You can remove certain characters, keep only one language, and declare data format to minimize human intervention.<br/>"
      }
    ]}
  />

  <section class="bg-f7f8fc"></section>
</PageLayout>
